        <abstract>
            <p>CD and family suggest inscriptions for Lyell memorial at Westminster Abbey.</p>
            <p>CD communicating H. Airy’s paper on phyllotaxis to the Royal Society.</p> 
<p>Frank observes pod-like emanations from glands of insectivorous plant ingesting solid insect particles [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10520</hi>].</p> 
        </abstract>
